-- Requirements -------------------------------------------------------

- gcc (compile with g++-4.x)
- make, automake, autoconf, libtool
- lib digital-scratch
- lib Boost.test

For Ubuntu 7.10 Gutsy:
    - see packages in INSTALL in digital-scratch directory
    - libboost-test-dev

For Ubuntu 9.04 Jaunty:
    - see packages in digital-scratch/documentation
    - libboost-test-dev

-- Build --------------------------------------------------------------

To build digital-scratch-test :
    - ./generate_configure_script.sh if you want to re-create configure
      script
    - ./configure
    - make clean all

-- Usage --------------------------------------------------------------

make check
or make check-quiet
or make check-log
or make check-random

